"```sql\nSELECT \n    SUM(cr.points) AS score, \n    c.name, \n    c.nationality\nFROM \n    constructorResults cr\nINNER JOIN \n    races r ON cr.raceId = r.raceId\nINNER JOIN \n    constructors c ON cr.constructorId = c.constructorId\nWHERE \n    r.name = 'Monaco Grand Prix' \n    AND r.year BETWEEN 1980 AND 2010\nGROUP BY \n    cr.constructorId\nORDER BY \n    score DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```"